headline: 3 Gas Distribution Stocks to Watch From a Flourishing Industry
summary: Increased natural gas export volumes and regular investment in pipelines are driving the Zacks Gas Distribution industry's near-term prospects. Utilities with stable infrastructure like ATO, MDU and NJR can provide reliable services to customers and benefit from a positive industry outlook.
